<br>
If the battle lasts 10+ mins then all your gonna do is drop mod rods during the fight.  Sure you could nuke, but when people dictate how you should play your class you won't be nuking for long.  You see shouts of &quot;Mages drop mod rods&quot; or get personalized tells of &quot;I need mod rods now!&quot;  <br>
<br>
Pets? Ha, yah right, you must be kidding.  Lure mobs = pet dead in a few AE's cuz the pet cannot resist it at all.  In fact any mob that AE's is pretty pointless to cast pets on, waste of mana.  Glad they changed the riposte code, perhaps pet resists will get worked on in the future.<br>
<br>
Wait till you hit luclin, some of those battles are so freaking long its not funny.  Better put that mod rod spell in the 1st slot cuz thats mostly what your gonna do.<br>
<br>
Once again, welcome to my life and thank god for Boots of Bladecalling.<br>
